## MarkerTechniqueParams.iconMayOverlap property

If `false`<!-- -->, the icon may overlap text and other icons of lower priority. If not defined, the property value from `textMayOverlap` will be used.  `false`

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
iconMayOverlap?: boolean;
```
